## üèóÔ∏è **Architecture Overview**

<div align="center">

```mermaid
graph TB
    A[User Input] --> B[Command Parser]
    B --> C[Context Engine]
    C --> D[Project Analysis]
    C --> E[Validation System]
    C --> F[AI Orchestrator]
    F --> G[Multi-Provider AI]
    F --> H[Tool Execution]
    H --> I[Checkpoint System]
    I --> J[Human Approval]
    J --> K[File Operations]
    K --> L[Result Display]
```

</div>

### **Key Components**

- **üß† Context Engine**: Complete project understanding and analysis
- **ü§ñ AI Orchestrator**: Multi-provider AI integration with streaming
- **‚è∞ Checkpoint System**: Time travel functionality with surgical undo
- **üõ°Ô∏è Validation System**: Prevents duplicates and breaking changes
- **üîê Human Approval**: Security-first approach to dangerous operations
- **‚öôÔ∏è Tool Ecosystem**: Extensible tool framework for file and terminal operations

